title: Meizu MX5 Goes on Pre-Order in Europe for €375 ($420)
text: It looks like Chinese handset maker Meizu has decided to bring its MX5 high-end Android smartphone to Europe. Meizu MX5 was initially launched in China a few months ago, but aside from India, it wasn't rolled out in other countries yet.
